                    <div class="service-details-content">
                        <div class="content-box-one">
                            <div class="inner">
                                <h3>7-Day Inner Self Realization</h3>
                                <h5>A Way To Enhance Yourselves</h5>                                
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="two-column">
                            <div class="row clearfix">
                                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 text-column">
                                    <div class="text">
                                    <p>This immersive 7-day program is designed to guide individuals on a journey of self-discovery and inner awakening. Through meditation, introspection, and yogic practices, participants learn to quiet the mind, understand their true nature, and cultivate lasting peace and clarity in daily life.</p>
                                    <p>Each day is thoughtfully structured to include guided sessions, reflective practices, and practical teachings that can be easily integrated into everyday routines. The program also helps in releasing mental stress, overcoming negative patterns, and developing a deeper sense of awareness and emotional balance. Participants are guided to reflect on the ultimate purpose of human birth, encouraging a deeper understanding of life beyond material pursuits.</p>
								<p>The program also emphasizes adopting a disciplined way of living, aligning daily actions with higher values and inner growth. Participants leave with simple yet powerful tools to continue their inner journey, leading to a more centered, purposeful, and harmonious way of living.</p>
                                                                             
